&lt;p&gt;Other client config:&lt;br/&gt;
 osc.fir-OST*.max_dirty_mb=256&lt;br/&gt;
 osc.fir-OST*.max_pages_per_rpc=1024&lt;br/&gt;
 osc.fir-OST*.max_rpcs_in_flight=8&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;I have a full lustre log during a slow dd on sh-ln05 that I have attached to this ticket.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Note: we are seeing the same behavior when using /fir (2.12 servers) and /oak (2.10 servers). This definitively seems to originate from the Lustre client itself.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;We also checked the state of IB and everything looks good.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Any idea on how to find out the root cause of this major random 2.12 client slowness ?&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Thanks!!&lt;br/&gt;
 Stephane&lt;/p&gt;</description>
